<subSubSection id="4AB7D3D1FF97FFACFF65FB86FDECFB4D" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0212805AFF97FFACFF65FB86FDECFB4D" blockId="6.[136,1452,567,1423]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFF65FB86FE8FFBDD" bold="true" box="[189,335,1108,1134]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Distribution</emphasis>
:— 
<taxonomicName id="C5ADFBD9FF97FFACFEABFB86FDD6FBDD" authorityName="Don" authorityYear="1823" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" box="[371,534,1108,1134]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Clidemia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Magnoliopsida" rank="species" species="hirta">
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFEABFB86FDD6FBDD" box="[371,534,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Clidemia hirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is widely distributed species from Central America to 
<collectingCountry id="7ABAC0CAFF97FFACFBACFB86FB23FBDD" box="[1140,1251,1108,1134]" name="Argentina" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFB29FB86FF05FB20" author="Baumgratz, J. F. A. &amp; Souza, M. L. D. R. &amp; Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A." pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="591 - 646" refId="ref22935" refString="Baumgratz, J. F. A., Souza, M. L. D. R., Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A. (2006) Melastomataceae na Reserva Biologica de Poco das Antas, Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro, Brasil: aspectos floristicos e taxonomicos. Rodriguesia 57 (3): 591 - 646." type="journal article" year="2006">
Baumgratz 
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFAACFB87FA6CFBDD" box="[1396,1452,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry id="7ABAC0CAFF97FFACFF2DFBAAFEF9FB21" box="[245,313,1144,1170]" name="Brazil" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Brazil</collectingCountry>
it is found in almost all states, usually in open areas, sunny and very anthropized habitats (
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFAF7FBAAFECBFB05" author="Baumgratz, J. F. A. &amp; Souza, M. L. D. R. &amp; Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A." pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="591 - 646" refId="ref22935" refString="Baumgratz, J. F. A., Souza, M. L. D. R., Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A. (2006) Melastomataceae na Reserva Biologica de Poco das Antas, Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro, Brasil: aspectos floristicos e taxonomicos. Rodriguesia 57 (3): 591 - 646." type="journal article" year="2006">
Baumgratz 
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFF50FB4FFF04FB05" box="[136,196,1180,1206]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFEC1FB4EFD45FB05" author="Michelangeli, F. A. &amp; Reginato, M." box="[281,645,1180,1206]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" refId="ref26186" refString="Michelangeli, F. A. &amp; Reginato, M. (2012) Clidemia. In: Baumgratz, J. F. A., Bernardo, K. F. R., Chiavegatto, B., Goldenberg, R., Guimaraes, P. J. F., Kriebel, R., Martins, A. B., Michelangeli, F. A., Reginato, M., Romero, R., Souza, M. L. D. R. &amp; Woodgyer, E. (Eds.) Melastomataceae: Lista de Especies da Flora do Brasil. Jardim Botanico do Rio de Janeiro. Available from: http: // floradobrasil. jbrj. gov. br / (accessed July 2012)." type="url" year="2012">Michelangeli &amp; Reginato 2012</bibRefCitation>
). It is classified as Vulnerable for the municipality of 
<collectingRegion id="C0694EB8FF97FFACFADAFB4EFA6BFB05" box="[1282,1451,1180,1206]" country="Brazil" name="Rio de Janeiro" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Rio de Janeiro</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFF48FB12FE91FB69" author="Baumgratz, J. F. A." box="[144,337,1216,1242]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="30 - 31" refId="ref22589" refString="Baumgratz, J. F. A. (2000) Melastomataceae. In: Di Maio, F. R. &amp; Silva, M. B. R. (Eds.) Especies ameacadas de extincao no municipio do Rio de Janeiro: flora e fauna. Secretaria Municipal de Meio Ambiente, Prefeitura da Cidade do Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro, pp. 30 - 31." type="book chapter" year="2000">Baumgratz 2000</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry id="7ABAC0CAFF97FFACFE5AFB12FE2BFB69" box="[386,491,1216,1242]" name="Malaysia" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
, Hawaii, 
<collectingCountry id="7ABAC0CAFF97FFACFD8EFB12FD7EFB69" box="[598,702,1216,1242]" name="Tanzania" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry id="7ABAC0CAFF97FFACFD20FB12FCBFFB69" box="[760,895,1216,1242]" name="Madagascar" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
it has become a naturalized weed (
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFAD2FB12FA67FB69" author="Almeda, F." box="[1290,1447,1216,1242]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="164 - 338" refId="ref21997" refString="Almeda, F. (2009) Melastomataceae. In: G. Davidse, M. Sousa-Sanchez, S. Knapp &amp; F. Chiang (Eds.) Flora Mesoamericana 4: 164 - 338." type="journal article" year="2009">Almeda 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFF50FB36FEE6FB4D" author="Gleason, H. A." box="[136,294,1252,1278]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="97 - 140" refId="ref24432" refString="Gleason, H. A. (1939) The genus Clidemia in Mexico and Central America. Brittonia 3 (2): 97 - 140. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 2804810" type="journal article" year="1939">Gleason 1939</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFEE8FB36FE18FB4D" author="Wurdack, J. J." box="[304,472,1252,1278]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="109 - 217" refId="ref28072" refString="Wurdack, J. J. (1962) Melastomataceae of Santa Catarina. Sellowia 14: 109 - 217." type="journal article" year="1962">Wurdack 1962</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFE3BFB36FDDFFB4D" author="Wurdack, J. J." box="[483,543,1252,1278]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" refId="ref28113" refString="Wurdack, J. J. (1980) Melastomataceae. In: Harling, G. &amp; Sparre, B. (Eds.) Flora of Equador, vol. 13. University Goteborg and Riksmuseum, Stocholm, 406 pp." type="book" year="1980">1980</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="4AB7D3D1FF97FFACFF65FADAFC0DFA3D" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="0212805AFF97FFACFF65FADAFC0DFA3D" blockId="6.[136,1452,567,1423]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFF65FADAFEFEFA91" bold="true" box="[189,318,1288,1314]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Comments</emphasis>
:—This is the first record for Marambaia, where 
<taxonomicName id="C5ADFBD9FF97FFACFC78FADAFC3EFA91" authorityName="Don" authorityYear="1823" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1753" box="[928,1022,1288,1314]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Clidemia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Magnoliopsida" rank="species" species="hirta">
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFC78FADAFC3EFA91" box="[928,1022,1288,1314]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">C. hirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
only occurs in Dense Submontane Ombrophilous Forest. It is distinguished mainly by the inner torus with an irregular tooth-fimbriated membranaceous ring, and calyx with slightly denticulate internal lobes or reduced to a membranaceous and sinuous ring. Additional illustrations in 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFEE8FAA7FDFEFA3C" author="Baumgratz, J. F. A. &amp; Souza, M. L. D. R. &amp; Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A." box="[304,574,1396,1423]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="591 - 646" refId="ref22935" refString="Baumgratz, J. F. A., Souza, M. L. D. R., Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A. (2006) Melastomataceae na Reserva Biologica de Poco das Antas, Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro, Brasil: aspectos floristicos e taxonomicos. Rodriguesia 57 (3): 591 - 646." type="journal article" year="2006">
Baumgratz 
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF97FFACFE6AFAA7FE2AFA3D" box="[434,490,1396,1422]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">et al.</emphasis>
(2006)
</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF97FFACFDA1FAA7FC08FA3D" author="Matsumoto, K. &amp; Martins, A. B." box="[633,968,1396,1423]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="19 - 22" refId="ref25752" refString="Matsumoto, K. A &amp; Martins, A. B. (2009) Clidemia. In: Wanderley, M. G. L., Shepherd, G. J., Melhem, T. S., Giulietti, A. M. &amp; Martins, S. E. (Eds.) Flora Fanerogamica do Estado de Sao Paulo, v. 6. Instituto de Botanica, FAPESP, Sao Paulo, pp. 19 - 22." type="book chapter" year="2009">Matsumoto &amp; Martins (2009)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
